Title: Dune Part Two
Description: Paul Atreides continues his mythical journey as he unites with Chani and the indigenous inhabitants of Arrakis, the Freman. They are on the warpath to take revenge on the conspirators who destroyed Paul's family. Faced with a choice between the love of his life and the fate of the known universe, Paul tries to prevent a terrible future that only he can foresee.

Title: Kung Fu Panda 4 (OV)
Description: After three life-threatening adventures in which he defeats the world's greatest villains with his unparalleled courage and insane fighting skills, an evil supervillain turns up: the Chameleon, who drops her little beady eyes on Po's Staff of Wisdom, with which she could retrieve all the great villains Po has sent to the spirit realm. With the help of the cunning thief Zhen, Po must protect the Valley of Peace. Gradually he discovers that heroes show up in the most unlikely places.

Title: Kung Fu Panda 4 (NL)
Description: Na drie levensgevaarlijke avonturen waarin hij de grootste schurken ter wereld verslaat met zijn ongekende moed en waanzinnige vechtkunsten, duikt een kwaadaardige superschurk op: de Kameleon, die haar kleine kraaloogjes laat vallen op Po’s Staf der Wijsheid, waarmee ze alle grote schurken die Po naar het geestenrijk heeft gestuurd terug zou kunnen halen. Met hulp van de sluwe dief Zhen moet Po de Vredesvallei beschermen. Gaandeweg ontdekt hij dat helden op de meest onwaarschijnlijke plekken opduiken.

Title: Anyone but You
Description: After an amazing first date, Bea and Ben's fiery attraction turns ice-cold--until they find themselves unexpectedly reunited at a wedding in Australia. So they do what any two mature adults would do: pretend to be a couple.

Title: Wonka
Description: Before opening the world's most famous chocolate factory, a young Willy Wonka dreams of becoming a candy maker. He sets off on an adventure and on his journey meets an imprisoned Oempa Loempa.

Title: Bob Marley: One Love
Description: One man. One message. One revolution. One legend. Bob Marley: One Love celebrates the life and music of an icon who inspired generations with his message of love and unity.

Title: Oppenheimer
Description: In the heart of World War II, physicist J. Robert Oppenheimer leads the clandestine Manhattan Project to develop the atomic bomb. As the project progresses, Oppenheimer confronts the moral dilemma of unleashing such destructive power. Tensions rise as he navigates political pressures and personal ethics, culminating in a race against time to determine the fate of humanity. Oppenheimer offers a gripping portrayal of one man's struggle with the consequences of scientific discovery in the face of war.

Title: Barbie
Description: Stereotypical Barbie experiences the perfect day every time, until one morning imperfections seem to occur to her. Determined to find her place in the world, she begins an adventurous journey through the real world.

Title: De Super Mario Bros. Movie (NL)
Description: Loodgieters en broers Mario en Luigi komen via een mysterieuze buis in een magische nieuwe wereld terecht, waar ze van elkaar gescheiden worden. Mario begint met hulp van prinses Peach aan een groots avontuur om zijn broer terug te vinden.

Title: De Super Mario Bros. Movie (OV)
Description: Plumbers and brothers Mario and Luigi enter a magical new world through a mysterious pipe, where they are separated from each other. Mario, with the help of Princess Peach, embarks on a grand adventure to find his brother again.

Title: Aquaman and the Lost Kingdom
Description: In an effort to end Black Manta's reign of terror, Aquaman forges an unlikely alliance to protect the kingdom and save the world from destruction.
